经跟保险公司制定了一个赔偿方案，但遗憾的是暂未与家长就此赔偿方案协商一致。目前仍在与家长沟通当中。 针对客人提出的客房内三角圆桌的安全问题，酒店已积极配合当地派出所完成了房间的检查，警方未对三角桌提出安全方面的质疑。同时，酒店工程总监已完成对每一间客房的三角圆桌的安全检查，“我们确认在正常使用下，此圆桌对于入住客人（包括儿童）并无安全隐患。”酒店将定期对客房内的桌椅和家具陈设进行维护检查，排除安全隐患。喜来登住客投诉称2岁孩子被砸伤，近乎毁容！酒店回应_澎湃号·媒体_澎湃新闻-The Paper"},"attached_info":"Cj8Igofn0+S2ufpuEAMaCTEwOTYwNjk3NSCUlaK1BjAAOD1AB3IJNjYyOTgxNTA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"132 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-53ed5a4b48cd2a1a536f1719e1a649cb_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1722478445.255685","card_id":"Q_412427628","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":412427628,"title":"在程序员从业生涯中，哪本书让你醍醐灌顶？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/412427628","type":"question","created":1596697693,"answer_count":64,"follower_count":1030,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[53,707,7897,26439,163487],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"欢迎大家畅所欲言推荐你们的私藏好书，随后我将也奉上华为专家大佬们的私房书单！"},"attached_info":"Cj8Igofn0+S2ufpuEAMaCDUzOTI3NzA0IN3YrvkFMAA4hghACHIJNDEyNDI3NjI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"101 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d86ee043b148b3b5e77a5e4c4f0f77c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1722478445.256099","card_id":"Q_663062071","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":663062071,"title":"职业「上新」，新增生成式人工智能系统应用员、用户增长运营师等 19 个新职业，反应了哪些职业趋势？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/66306207